      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，我刚才的描述可能有问题。DiagnosticEngine在流程中出现了两次——它既是起点，又是EMR_Sync之后的回环节点。这样画会不会让人困惑？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确实，目前图里有两个DiagnosticEngine节点。从业务上看，这是同一个引擎实例吗？还是您希望表示两次不同的处理阶段？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "是同一个引擎，我搞错了。请把结构改成：DiagnosticEngine → EMR_Sync，然后EMR_Sync直接连到LabAnalyzer，中间不要回环到DiagnosticEngine。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "收到，我修正一下：去掉EMR_Sync到DiagnosticEngine的回环，改为EMR_Sync直接流向LabAnalyzer。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "修正完成。现在的流程是：DiagnosticEngine启动诊断，同步EMR，直接进入LabAnalyzer分析，最后归档到PatientRecords。这样逻辑清晰多了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
